OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Fsome light and patchy rain during the
OL,7,Fevening. Clear spells then developing,
OL,8,Fbefore further cloud and rain arrives
OL,9,Ffrom the west towards dawn, this
OL,10,Fpersistent and occasionally heavy.
OL,11,FBecoming breezy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FBreezy with rain, heavy at
OL,14,Ftimes, this clearing away eastwards by
OL,15,Fearly afternoon. Sunny spells then
OL,16,Fdeveloping, also isolated blustery
OL,17,Fheavy showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
